01:11:34,373 --> 01:11:40,545
Eventually, the AIG bailout cost taxpayers over $1 50 billion.

1117
01:11:40,713 --> 01:11:44,090
A hundred and sixty billion dollars went through AlG.

1118
01:11:44,258 --> 01:11:47,051
Fourteen billion went to Goldman Sachs.

1119
01:11:47,219 --> 01:11:50,430
At the same time, Paulson and Geithner forced AlG -

1120
01:11:50,597 --> 01:11:54,559
- to surrender its right to sue Goldman and the other banks for fraud.

1121
01:11:54,727 --> 01:11:59,772
Isn't there a problem when the person in charge of dealing with this crisis -

1122
01:11:59,940 --> 01:12:02,108
- is the former CEO of Goldman Sachs?

1123
01:12:02,276 --> 01:12:05,862
Someone who had a major role in causing it.

1124
01:12:06,030 --> 01:12:08,740
It's fair to say that the financial markets today -

1125
01:12:08,907 --> 01:12:10,742
- are incredibly complicated.

1126
01:12:10,909 --> 01:12:12,618
--and supply urgently needed money - .

1127
01:12:12,786 --> 01:12:15,038
On October 4th, 2008 -

1128
01:12:15,205 --> 01:12:19,250
- President Bush signs a 700-billion-dollar bailout bill.

1129
01:12:19,418 --> 01:12:21,753
But world stock markets continue to fall -

1130
01:12:21,920 --> 01:12:24,756
- amid fears that a global recession is now underway.

1131
01:12:30,095 --> 01:12:33,389
The bailout legislation does nothing to stem the tide of layoffs -

1132
01:12:33,557 --> 01:12:35,350
- and foreclosures.

1133
01:12:35,517 --> 01:12:40,605
Unemployment in the United States and Europe rises to 1 0 percent.

1134
01:12:40,773 --> 01:12:44,108
The recession accelerates and spreads globally.

1135
01:12:47,946 --> 01:12:52,200
I began to get really scared because l hadn't foreseen -

1136
01:12:52,368 --> 01:12:56,954
- the whole world going down at the same rate at the same time.

1137
01:12:57,623 --> 01:12:59,457
By December of 2008 -

1138
01:12:59,625 --> 01:13:03,127
- General Motors and Chrysler are facing bankruptcy.

1139
01:13:03,462 --> 01:13:06,214
And as U.S. consumers cut back on spending -

1140
01:13:06,382 --> 01:13:09,926
- Chinese manufacturers see sales plummet.

1141
01:13:10,969 --> 01:13:15,473
