1455
01:32:45,476 --> 01:32:50,021
I think it's certainly important to disclose the - .

1456
01:32:55,528 --> 01:32:57,696
Well, l think that's also a little different -

1457
01:32:57,863 --> 01:33:01,825
- from cases that we're talking about here because - .

